  "title": "SALES ADMIN",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><ol><li>Liaise with customers & relevant parties</li><li>Attend to phone calls and email enquiries</li><li>Liaise closely with Finance/ Admin Team & Project/ Service Team</li><li>Prepare tender proposals, cost estimations, quotation</li></ol><p>Requirements:</p><ol><li>Diploma or equivalent</li><li>1 to 2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications (Excel, Word)</li><li>Meticulous, with good communication skills</li><li>Team player with ability to work closely with internal and external customer needs effectively</li><li>Independent with initiative and drive to be proactive in operational activities to meet customer expectations</li><li>Preferably with relevant experience in sound & visual communication system industries</li></ol><p>Notes about ISPL:</p><ul><li>ISPL is an equal opportunities employer.</li><li>See www.ispl.com for more details of the company.</li><li>ISPL is an SME working environment</li><li>Entry-level candidates with relevant work experience are welcome. </li></ul>",
